Package: prostPostprocess
Type: Package
Title: Provide utility fonction to postprocess prost! output
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Léo Milhade
Maintainer: Léo Milhade <leo.milhade@irisa.fr>
Description: prostPostprocess provides a collection of function to help process
    data from prost! (https://www.nature.com/articles/s41598-019-40361-8) in 
    order to do a differential analysis.
    The process consists in three steps :
    - Load and filter read counts and metadata
    - Create a DESeqDataset compatible with DESeq2
    - Plot the results of a differential analysis with DESeq
